name: "The Heart" Tee
description: The heart transcends physical, emotional and spiritual boundaries. Its beauty is in its ability to multitask: power the body, harness the magic of love and support the palpitations of life. The heart is the most critical part of our being yet keeping it safe is our greatest challenge.
